Hypogonadism in Wegener's granulomatosis.

Richter JG(1), Becker A, Specker C, Schneider M.

Author information:
(1)Department of Endocrinology, Diabetes and Rheumatology, Rheumatology Section, 
University Hospital Düsseldorf, D 40225 Düsseldorf, Germany. 
