Author information:
(1)Eating Disorders Program, St. Paul's Hospital, University of British 
Columbia, Vancouver, BC, Canada V6Z 1Y6.

BACKGROUND: There are numerous reports of the standardized mortality ratio (SMR) 
of anorexia nervosa (AN). However, the life expectancy of AN, has not been 
reported.
OBJECTIVE: To estimate the average life expectancy of patients who are diagnosed 
with AN at various ages.
